                    <desc>
                    Colophon This book was begun on the fourth of Säne and finished on the thirtieth of Yäkkatit. This book of the prophet Ezekiel in Ge’ez and Amharic was commissioned by Nǝburä ‘Ǝdǝ Dǝmeṭǝros Gäbrä Maryam, whose baptismal name is Kinä Śǝlasie, and the name of his mother is Wälätä Ab. It is written in 1949 EC (=1956/57)
